      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Quick and simple uploading:</strong>
        </li>
        <li>With Silverpeas, users can  upload contents simply and quickly, directly to a website, without the need for specialist web or IT skills.</li>
        <li>The web designer can build a website with standard tools (Adobe DreamweaverÂ®) and use a tag library for positioning the contents on pages (statically or dynamically).</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Dynamic contents:</strong>
        </li>
        <li>The web design is independent from the content format.</li>
        <li>The content can be presented on different websites.</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Visibility and online display control:</strong>
        </li>
        <li>Using the classification scheme, it is possible to choose on which pages the content will be visible. Only content declared as 
          <em>visible</em> on the web will be displayed on web pages.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Validation workflow:</strong>
        </li>
        <li>The publication process can be organised around a validation workflow.</li>
      </ul>
